data.description: Great home with room for everyone! Flexible floorplan has two first floor bedrooms, including the primary suite. Additional room would make a great study. Formal dining could also be office space. The second floor has a game room, three additional bedrooms and a bathroom. Convenient location in Mansfield's desirable Legacy High area. All levels of schools are within a 2 mile radius. The home has great flow with the kitchen open to the family room and breakfast area. Kitchen features a breakfast bar, pantry, and granite countertops. Oven and microwave replaced July 2023. Step out onto the expansive deck and discover the perfect spot for summer fun and relaxation. An above ground pool adds a refreshing touch, and there's still plenty of yard space for play and pets. There are covered and open patio areas where you can unwind and entertain, plus a storage shed. Roof replaced in 2019 and upstairs HVAC units replaced in 2023.
